text: Hikaru Sulu is a fictional character in the television and movie franchise Star Trek. He is a lieutenant of the Starship Enterprise.George Takei, Mr. Sulu of Star Trek, Comes Out and Speaks Out Sulu is played by actor George Takei and by John Cho. ==References== Category:Star Trek: The Original Series characters Category:Fictional characters introduced in 1966
title: Hikaru Sulu
